Title: MADZEE ISRO - CHANDRAYAAN 3 PATCHWORK DENIM UNISEX JACKET - BLACK (100% COTTON)
Description:
A tribute to Indian space exploration- ISRO and our first ever moon landing. Introducing our Isro Chandrayaan 3 Denim Patchwork Jacket.  A must have denim jacket for every Indian who takes pride in our space achievements.
Every patch is a testament to ISRO’s ingenuity, curiosity and perseverance to achieve the unachievable.
This jacket is made with high-quality denim fabric that is 100% cotton. The design features a button-front closure, patchwork and a stylish collar.
The versatile all weather jacket allows you to effortlessly dress it up or down for any occasion offering style that stands out. 
If you want to own a piece of history or just shout out “I saw it land” , get this ISRO Chandrayaan 3  denim jacket, available online exclusively at Groovee.
